data.description: Price reduction. Great starter home! Functional, well kept, three bed, two bath home in central Cleburne. This home struts luxury vinyl plank throughout and carpet in bedrooms. Eat-in kitchen with tile countertops and open to the utility room. Master bedroom has a walk in closet with separate shower and toilet. Garage conversion allows space for game room or home gym. Large fenced backyard with open porch and a storage shed. Work out equipment will stay with the property if Buyer desires. Bring all offers!
